snippet.title: SKIBIDI BACKROOMS - Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description: SKIBIDI BACKROOMS is a cooperative horror game for a group of 4 players. Solo mode is also available. You have to survive among the BACKROOMS and find a way out before you are overtaken by the SKIBIDI TOILET. Updates and various interesting things await you...
